The paper discusses the security properties of mmWave transmissions, which is a topic related to both computer security (cs.CR) and networking (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the technical aspects of mmWave transmissions, such as antenna arrays and signal processing, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper proposes defenses against side-lobe eavesdropping attacks, which is a topic related to systems and control (cs.SY).
